# Work Week In Review

When running `Op Reports/work_week_in_review.py`:

- **Current period** always starts on **Sunday** and ends on the report end date (Friday on Saturday runs; today on Sun–Fri runs).
- **Prior period** is the **previous Sunday–Friday**, with the same day-count when the current week is partial.
- Run from the `Op Reports` folder: `python3 work_week_in_review.py`
- Optional override: `python3 work_week_in_review.py --end YYYY-MM-DD`
- Do **not** use trailing `--days` windows; the script encodes Sun–Fri logic.

Example (end Friday 2026-06-12): current `2026-06-07 .. 2026-06-12`, prior `2026-05-31 .. 2026-06-05`.
